A fourth year (MMath) unit that goes into more depth on numerical methods for solving ODEs.

[Runge-Kutta Methods Lecture Notes](/files/notes/Adv_ODEs.pdf){:target="_blank"}

<!--more-->

Topics include:

- the derivation of Runge-Kutta methods using trees
- adaptive step size control
- implicit Runge-Kutta method
- Newton's method for systems of nonlinear equations
- stability and order stars
- the n-body problem.
